Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  好痛啊  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢小博了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从第一次遇见的时候开始就决定是小博了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想这就是恋爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一见钟情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  渐渐地就忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆  就把小博…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.15,0:01:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  这是初恋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于知道了恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做那样的事  你认为是恋爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你…
